id: Should the following moments in time be included on Hypha’s official and publicly available timeline?
1: We launched Distributed.Press and its sister project COMPOST Magazine.
2: We started our initial work in the Cosmos ecosystem.
3: We completed our first piece of work on the Starling Lab initiative.
4: The first of our founding members were able to work at Hypha full-time.
5: Two of Hypha’s original founding members resigned from the cooperative.
